'''韋斯利·泰倫特·斯奈普斯'''（{{lang-en|Wesley Trent Snipes}}，{{bd|1962年|7月31日|}}）是一名美國男演員、製片人和武術家。他本身痴迷武术，12歲已經開始習武，先後取得[[空手道|空手道]][[松濤館流|松濤館流]]黑帶五段和[[合氣道|合氣道]]黑帶二段的資格，跟隨維埃拉大師（{{lang|en|Mestre Jelon Vieira}}）學習[[巴西戰舞|巴西戰舞]]<ref name="independent.co.uk">{{cite news |title=Wesley Snipes: Action man courts a new beginning |work=The Independent |location=London |date=2010-06-04 |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/wesley-snipes-action-man-courts-a-new-beginning-1991437.html |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126061833/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/wesley-snipes-action-man-courts-a-new-beginning-1991437.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，亦曾經進行[[中國功夫|中國功夫]]、[[巴西柔術|巴西柔術]]及[[踢拳|踢拳]]等多種武術訓練<ref>{{cite news |title=Neighborhood Report: Greenwich Village; This Monk Is a Boldface Name |work=New York Times |date=2006-05-14 |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E06EFDE143EF937A25756C0A9609C8B63 |accessdate=2010-03-01 |first=Peter |last=Ritter |archive-date=2017-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802083936/https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E06EFDE143EF937A25756C0A9609C8B63 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他最為人熟悉的電影作品是飾演[[漫威漫畫|漫威漫畫]]電影《[[刀鋒戰士_(電影)|刀鋒戰士]]》（1998年至2004年）三部曲的男主角<ref>{{cite news|url=http://comicbook.com/2015/07/09/welsey-snipes-has-met-with-marvel-about-returning-as-blade-the-v/|title=Wesley Snipes has met with Marvel about returning as Blade the vampire hunter in Cinematic Universe|date=2015-07-09|accessdate=2015-07-29|archive-date=2015-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150710074429/http://comicbook.com/2015/07/09/welsey-snipes-has-met-with-marvel-about-returning-as-blade-the-v/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 早年生活 ==
韋斯利生於[[美國|美國]][[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]][[奧蘭多_(佛羅里達州)|奧蘭多]]，母親瑪麗安（{{lang|en|Maryann}}）是助教，父親韋斯利·魯道夫·斯奈普斯（{{lang|en|Wesley Rudolph Snipes}}）是飛機工程師<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-7278956_ITM | work=Knight Ridder/Tribune | title=1ST PERSON: Meet Wesley Snipes | first1=Alisa | last1=LaVelle | first2=Michelle | last2=Buzgon | date=2000-08-09 | accessdate=2015-07-29 | archive-date=2012-07-18 | archive-url=https://archive.is/20120718064736/www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-7278956_ITM | dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在[[紐約|紐約]][[布朗克斯|布朗克斯]]長大，高中時主修音樂和表演藝術，曾短暫遷回[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]，大學再重回紐約，在[[紐約州立大學|紐約州立大學]]帕切斯學院完成學位。

== 逃稅風波 ==
2006年，韋斯利曾捲入一宗[[逃稅|逃稅]]風波。他被美國政府指控串謀[[詐騙|詐騙]]、明知而作出或協助及教唆他人作出虛假和欺詐性的索償、及未提交聯邦{{link-en|報稅表|Tax return}}，當中涉及稅務款項數以千萬美元計<ref>Superseding Indictment, October 12, 2006, ''United States v. Wesley Trent Snipes'', entry 6, page 8, paragraphs 29 & 30 and page 9, paragraph 39, case no. 5:06-cr-00022-WTH-GRJ, [[United_States_District_Court_for_the_Middle_District_of_Florida|United States District Court for the Middle District of Florida]] (Ocala Div.).</ref>。審訊延續了四年多的時間，韋斯利的上訴最後被駁回，判刑三年<ref>Order List, p. 2, ''certiorari denied'', ''Wesley T. Snipes v. United States'', case no. 10-1075, [[United_States_Supreme_Court|United States Supreme Court]] (June 6, 2011).</ref><ref>Lee Ross, "Supreme Court Won't Hear Wesley Snipes Tax Evasion Appeal," June 6, 2011, Fox News, at [http://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/2011/06/06/supreme-court-wont-hear-wesley-snipes-tax-evasion-appeal/?test=faces] {{Wayback|url=http://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/2011/06/06/supreme-court-wont-hear-wesley-snipes-tax-evasion-appeal/?test=faces |date=20160307220459 }}.</ref><ref>Bill Mears, "High court dismisses actor's appeal on tax evasion conviction," June 6, 2011, CNN, at [http://www.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/06/06/scotus.wesley.snipes/] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/06/06/scotus.wesley.snipes/ |date=20181216210941 }}.</ref>。他於2010年琅璫入獄，至2013年刑滿出獄<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/04/05/showbiz/wesley-snipes-released/ |title=Actor Wesley Snipes released from prison |publisher=CNN |date=2013-04-05 |accessdate=2013-04-06 |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130055614/https://www.cnn.com/2013/04/05/showbiz/wesley-snipes-released/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
重獲自由後第一部電影《[[轟天猛將3|轟天猛將3]]》的第一幕就是[[史泰龍|史泰龍]]等人將被困於囚車的韋斯利騎劫出來，韋斯利亦將整個監獄炸為平地，借電影情節發洩一番，同時在劇中調侃自己。

